data.description: This lovely property is located in an established neighborhood and offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a 1 car garage. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the main living area features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or spending time with family. The kitchen boasts ample counter and cabinet space, all open to the dining area. The bedrooms offer plenty of room for relaxation and rest. The primary bedroom features an attached half-bath for added convenience. The full bathroom has been beautifully updated with modern finishes and is sure to impress.  Step outside into your expansive backyard which provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, and more, with a large storage building on a concrete slab. Imagine spending your evenings under the stars, gathered around a fire pit with loved ones. This home is move-in ready and waiting for you to make it your own. Contact us today to schedule your showing!
